Module: snowball
Title: Snowball
Author: Martin Porter <martin@tartarus.org>
Maintainer: Richard Boulton <richard@tartarus.org>
Description: Snowball is a small string processing language designed for creating stemming algorithms for use in Information Retrieval.  This module contains both the snowball compiler, stemming algorithms for several languages, and a library providing a simple interface to the main algorithms.
Homepage: http://snowball.tartarus.org/
Status: Active
